{
  "stem": "10572.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And you don't ever have to worry of going to America.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That was in 1937.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "A year later, when he was on his way to Buchenwald and after he came out of Buchenwald, he  had changed his tune a little bit and wasn't quite sure if the God that he had served for so many years as the head of the congregation was really alive and if he could really trust him.",
      "word_count": 57
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he thought of a possibility of going, packing up the next day and going to Shanghai.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Shanghai was the only place where people could go without visa.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And many of them went.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "This is-- gives you a little bit of a cliche of what went on, particularly among the well-situated and integrated members of German Jews.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I was at that time, in '37, I was still, I was still hoping that, that it would all blow up and that we could continue.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But little by little, I started to realize that I better concentrated on my education, on my technical education, not with the view that someday I would take over my father's firm, but so that I use this hard come by technical skill and develop it so that some day, if I would have to leave Germany without a penny, that I would be able to support myself.",
      "word_count": 68
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, not yet.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then things started to move fast.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, Hitler had come--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were-- you know, there was a political turmoil in Germany.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a fight between-- we, in the first place, had this ridiculous system of multi, multi, multi parties.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had, at that point, we had maybe 25 political parties.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And from the center in the Democratic Party and the Social Democrats, you had the extremes of the, of the Nazis on one side and the communists on the other side.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And those with the two strongest parties besides the Social Democrats.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In, in 1930-- in 1919, in 1929, I remember I was on my way to school.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they won, the Nazis won their first tremendous victory in the Reichstag.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But then things calmed down.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, and the economic situation became a little better.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And again, the wishful thinkers thought maybe Hitler has lost the, the, the thing that moved him ahead by, by the wisdom of the democratic government.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And therefore, maybe it will not happen.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, I think I experienced the, the, the primitive anti-Semitism of, of, of the anti-social or asocial elements in our society, in German society.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I say in our society.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were kids when I was 14, 15 years old who used to call me a, a Jew or dirty Jew.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I went at that time, I joined, I joined in a boxing society, a boxing club, in order to learn how to physically defend myself against the attacks of those.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pardon me?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mhm.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But, but it was part of, of growing up.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, if, if, if I wouldn't have been a Jew, they would have called me a dirty Catholic, you know.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But other words, these were elements that would have picked on anybody that they felt inferior to.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But it was not an, it was not a destructive force in my life.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In fact, anti-Semitism was never a destructive force in my life.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I think that it was, in many ways, by turning it around, in many, many ways a positive force.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I think I tried much harder to be a better human being and to be a more skilled human being because of the threat of anti-Semitism.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I have said sometimes in retrospect, many years later, after Buchenwald, said that I would never be able to go through it again.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But I wouldn't have sold the experience I had in Buchenwald for any money, because I thought it gave me a new standard of survival.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It gave me a new test.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I remember when, later on, when I went into  the American Arm and I was in basic training, and there were guys who were bitching about the toughness of our basic training.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I was laughing inside.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I thought, little do they know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And had new, I had learned a minimum of survival, which they had never experienced.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They were spoiled kids.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I had been taught the hard way this lesson that I think stayed with me all through my life.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
